This is a recipe that is not even a recipe, but I just want to share it with you all because it makes great finger food for babies and this is just to give you an idea. So try this out, and this is not only for babies, it makes a great breakfast for adults as well.
&nbsp;
Preparat

I spread some Nutella over the bread and coated it with an eggless custard mix and fried it. It was delicious. Instead of the custard powder mix, you can use egg coating as well.&nbsp;
I hope you will give this a try and let me know how it turns out for you.
